name: Surgical Steel Tongue Bar
description:
The bars are 2.5cm long, with 0.6cm balls.
We will send you a random coloured one, unless you want a specific colour then you can message us requesting it!

You will also recieve a couple of free stickers and a sweetie too! :)

name: Assorted Perler Bead Necklace!
description: Here we have some hand made perler bead necklaces. These are some of our designs so far, but we will take any requests. You can either request one of the necklaces that are there but in different colours, or a completely different design with a range of colours! The pendant will be on a 24" silver plated chain too :) When you come to order one of these necklaces, it will say "add special instructions to merchant", here you must type what pendant you want and in which colours, or we won't know what to send to you! You will also recieve a couple of free stickers and a sweetie too :)!

name: Rubix Cube Necklace!
description:
Fully working rubix cube on a 24" silver plated chain :)
The rubix cube is 3cm x 3cm!

You will also recieve a couple of free stickers and a sweetie too :)!
